# =====================================================================
# This git repo holds ONLY the server-side parts of SmartTds:
#   - SmartTdsApi/   (the ASP.NET Core API)
#   - _migration/    (PostgreSQL schema/seed/licensing + deploy scripts)
# The WinForms desktop and the other solution projects are intentionally
# NOT tracked here (they stay in the full SVN working copy).
# =====================================================================

# ignore everything at the root...
/*
# ...except these:
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/SmartTdsApi/
!/_migration/

# build output & temp (inside the kept folders)
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/publish_linux/
*.zip

# secrets & generated artifacts — NEVER commit
**/smarttds.env
**/*.local.json
_migration/tools/_*.sql
